OL,3,CFormer Tesco worker settles claims
OL,4,Cover handling of sexual harassment for
OL,5,C#45k
OL,7,FA former Tesco employee has settled
OL,8,Fher claims against the supermarket
OL,9,Fgiant over their handling of sexual
OL,10,Fharassment and victimisation for
OL,11,F#45,000.
OL,13,FThe settlement has been reached with
OL,14,Fno admission of liability.
OL,16,FInternational power-lifter Lara
OL,17,FStorey, now 23, worked part-time as a
OL,18,FDotcom Personal Shopper while studying
OL,19,Fat university.
