OL,3,CFormer Tesco worker settles claims
OL,4,Cover handling of sexual harassment for
OL,5,C#45k
OL,7,FShe claimed that she had been
OL,8,Fsubjected to sexual harassment by a
OL,9,Fcolleague which included unwanted
OL,10,Fphysical touching and a bombardment of
OL,11,Finappropriate messages, and Ms Storey
OL,12,Fsays she emphatically told the
OL,13,Fcolleague to stop on a number of
OL,14,Foccasions.
OL,16,FDespite this, she said the colleague
OL,17,Fshe had complained about remained in
OL,18,Fpost even though she had been
OL,19,Freassured that the person in question
OL,20,Fwould be retrained or relocated to
OL,21,Fanother department or store.
