OL,7,FShe said she then raised a grievance
OL,8,Fwith her employer, which was upheld.
OL,10,FA complaint was lodged at the Office
OL,11,Fof the Industrial Tribunal, but Ms
OL,12,FStorey contended that after doing
OL,13,Fthis, she felt that she was then
OL,14,Fvictimised and treated unfairly by
OL,15,Fmore senior staff.
OL,17,FMs Storey eventually resigned from her
OL,18,Fjob with Tesco.
