OL,7,FShe was supported by the Equality
OL,8,FCommission for Northern Ireland in
OL,9,Ftaking the case which was settled
OL,10,Fwithout admission of liability.
OL,12,FMs Storey said she felt she had to
OL,13,Fchallenge what happened.
OL,15,F"I wish none of this had ever
OL,16,Fhappened," she said.
OL,18,F"I was a student working my way
OL,19,Fthrough university. I didn't ask for
OL,20,Fany of this. I had to challenge it and
OL,21,FI'm glad I did.
