OL,7,F"I want other women to know that they
OL,8,Fdon't have to accept this type of
OL,9,Fbehaviour or treatment, and they
OL,10,Fshould expect to be treated fairly by
OL,11,Ftheir employer."
OL,13,FGeraldine McGahey, Chief Commissioner
OL,14,Fof the Equality Commission for
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland, said everyone has
OL,16,Fthe right to be treated with dignity
OL,17,Fand respect at work.
