OL,7,F"Our sex discrimination laws are
OL,8,Falmost 50 years old, and
OL,9,Funfortunately, they are needed as much
OL,10,Ftoday as they did when they were first
OL,11,Fintroduced," she said.
OL,13,F"Everyone has the right to be treated
OL,14,Fwith dignity and respect at work.
OL,16,F"Employers must ensure that, where
OL,17,Ftheir employees fail to live up to
OL,18,Fthat standard, action is taken to deal
OL,19,Fwith it effectively and that employees
OL,20,Fare dealt with or supported
OL,21,Fappropriately.
