OL,7,F"It is imperative therefore that
OL,8,Femployers have policies and procedures
OL,9,Fin place to manage these situations
OL,10,Feffectively and that their managers
OL,11,Fare trained to use them."
OL,13,FThe Equality Commission said that
OL,14,FTesco has also agreed to liaise with
OL,15,Fthe Equality Commission to review its
OL,16,Fpolicies, practices and procedures on
OL,17,Fharassment.
